717
00:50:48,448 --> 00:50:51,685
A man who's friendly
and constantly expressing love.

718
00:50:53,453 --> 00:50:54,354
Another X.

719
00:50:54,821 --> 00:50:57,124
- Why?
- Isn't that nice?

720
00:50:57,391 --> 00:51:00,661
They'll give you a hard time for the rest
of your lives with a woman problem.

721
00:51:01,161 --> 00:51:02,663
Seriously, that girl...

722
00:51:03,397 --> 00:51:04,965
It's so hard.

723
00:51:05,432 --> 00:51:08,702
