Is that for your granddaughter?

811
00:58:03,884 --> 00:58:05,385
Granddaughter?

812
00:58:07,221 --> 00:58:10,157
Yes. My granddaughter.

813
00:58:11,558 --> 00:58:14,795
I'm looking for something
for my granddaughter.

814
00:58:17,297 --> 00:58:19,132
What's her size?

815
00:58:25,606 --> 00:58:28,609
Take this as my last warning and behave.

816
00:58:30,277 --> 00:58:34,014
Return to the dorm as soon as possible.

817
00:58:34,014 --> 00:58:35,449
There isn't much time left.

818
00:58:40,320 --> 00:58:41,421
My goodness.

819
00:58:43,524 --> 00:58:46,126
Stop it. What if someone sees us?

820
00:58:46,126 --> 00:58:47,761
I already told you many times!

821
00:58:47,761 --> 00:58:50,097
It's not like we're an old man
and a young lady anymore.

822
00:58:50,097 --> 00:58:51,632
So what if someone sees us?

823
00:58:51,632 --> 00:58:53,600
Don't try to ruin my future.

824
00:58:53,600 --> 00:58:55,969
My agency told me to behave.

825
00:58:55,969 --> 00:58:58,472
If I act rashly again, I might get fired.

826
00:59:02,342 --> 00:59:03,377
Go now.

827
00:59:08,048 --> 00:59:09,116
It's you again.

828
00:59:11,051 --> 00:59:12,753
- What are you doing?
- What?

829
00:59:14,288 --> 00:59:16,690
No, I was just...

830
00:59:16,690 --> 00:59:18,058
We were talking as you can see.

831
00:59:22,229 --> 00:59:23,297
Talking?

832
00:59:29,803 --> 00:59:31,438
Why did you lose so much weight?

833
00:59:33,674 --> 00:59:35,242
Are you sure they're not exploiting you?

834
00:59:36,577 --> 00:59:37,477
Go home.

835
00:59:38,979 --> 00:59:40,380
- What?
- Go.

836
00:59:41,081 --> 00:59:43,016
That's up to her.

837
00:59:43,984 --> 00:59:45,786
A trainee isn't your employee.

838
00:59:47,721 --> 00:59:49,423
You've only met her once.

839
00:59:49,423 --> 00:59:51,592
Who are you to cross the line?

840
00:59:52,226 --> 00:59:53,861
I can always get to know her.

841
00:59:54,862 --> 00:59:57,331
We turned out to be neighbors.
Maybe we're meant to be.

842
00:59:57,331 --> 00:59:59,433
Stop the lame jokes.

843
01:00:00,400 --> 01:00:01,401
Stay away from her.

844
01:00:01,835 --> 01:00:03,337
- What?
- What's wrong?

845
01:00:03,337 --> 01:00:05,739
He's obviously a stalker.

846
01:00:05,739 --> 01:00:06,874
It's best...

847
01:00:07,908 --> 01:00:09,443
to eradicate stalkers early.

848
01:00:09,443 --> 01:00:11,712
What? Stalkers? Eradicate?

849
01:00:12,212 --> 01:00:14,014
Are you done?

850
01:00:14,014 --> 01:00:15,782
If I keep going,
it won't be in words anymore.

851
01:00:17,451 --> 01:00:18,485
Seriously...

852
01:00:44,077 --> 01:00:46,346
(Who Is She!)

853
01:00:46,346 --> 01:00:47,681
Do you really want to do this?

854
01:00:47,681 --> 01:00:48,916
You started it.

855
01:00:48,916 --> 01:00:49,783
That's so cold.

856
01:00:49,783 --> 01:00:50,918
Do you want to take this to the end?

857
01:00:50,918 --> 01:00:51,919
I'll tell you the truth.

858
01:00:51,919 --> 01:00:53,120
Stop it.

859
01:00:53,387 --> 01:00:54,655
He is...

860
01:00:54,655 --> 01:00:57,324
The menu and the presentation.
It's Mother's food.

861
01:00:57,324 --> 01:00:59,293
Since when were you left-handed?

862
01:00:59,293 --> 01:01:01,695
O Mal Soon?

863
01:01:01,695 --> 01:01:04,431
Did you have fun playing with us
until now?

864
01:01:04,431 --> 01:01:07,334
You don't stop people
from going on dates, do you?

865
01:01:07,868 --> 01:01:10,470
Is he flirting with me?

866
01:01:10,704 --> 01:01:13,507
I didn't realize it
when everyone else could see it.

867
01:01:13,507 --> 01:01:15,075
Anyway, I'm not going to break it anymore.
